Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情怎么会搞成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拿马被攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JOSH-A的成功还有何意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拿马补给线被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球迟早难保
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不是反击战役的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回维多利亚的作战还在筹备中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但想完好无损的夺回质量加速器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕难度非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布呢 奥布怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然再三要求征用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个顽固的乌兹米·纳拉·阿斯哈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死活不肯点头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？ 就因为是…中立？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙儿在战场上拼得你死我活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗击人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兹拉尔 请注意措辞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是蓝色宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多有冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位还对那个假惺惺的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此宽容大度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候能不能保持中立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经由不得他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布好歹是个主权国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能强求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为地球上的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布理应协助联合国
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么我亲自出马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出面与奥布交涉？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之眼下最重要的是搞到质量加速器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越快越好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者取其一 或者全部得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位还要策划维多利亚港的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分担来做效率更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:02:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且说不定还有机会测试它们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道打算动用那些机体？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得看对方的态度了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位阿斯哈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真如传闻中那样冥顽不化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 他也许会有点麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:50.48,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1180,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}炮火的决断
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.35,0:03:50.48,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1180,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}炮火的决断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:03:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城坂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后通牒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如继续对世界情势置若罔闻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为地球国家却欲独善其身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持所谓“中立”立场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒不协助备战的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联合军将代表其成员国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向贵国要求如下内容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  奥布联合首长国现政权立即解散
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  解除武装并解散军队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若48小时内无法做到如下要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联合将视奥布为扎夫特援助国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付诸武力进行讨伐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拿马被攻陷后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不顾体面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大西洋联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平洋联邦舰队已开始南下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想要的是质量加速器和曙光社
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算揭露他们的强盗行径
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有国家敢反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧亚联盟元气大伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤道联合和斯堪蒂纳维亚王国等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经保持中立的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现也已经倒向联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也到了必须作出选择的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知事态的扎夫特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从卡本塔里亚基地发来了会谈邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要把世界一分为二吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大西洋联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非敌即友 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布就要这样抛弃理念与法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人之命 与无冤无仇的敌人战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投靠联邦 PLANT就是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投靠PLANT 联邦就是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在屈服于联邦 避免眼前的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就会成为第二个巴拿马！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论加入哪个阵营 也难逃战火！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先下令避难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禾木拉代表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何必须避免
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们成为时代的牺牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马鲁奇奥导师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 全体船员集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府将有重大事项发表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请全体国民注意收听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在地球军舰队正朝奥布进发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不加入地球军 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同抗击扎夫特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要被视为扎夫特援助国
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是出兵理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布政府为贯彻中立立场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍在继续外交上的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 仅从地球军的行动来看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须承认 战斗几乎无法避免
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布已经命令全体国民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤离城市及军事设施
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防不测 进入防卫状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也同样 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面临着选择
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号作为一艘逃舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话立场微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对奥布的事态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该如何自处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既没有人命令我们 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有命令你们的权限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果最终斡旋失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天早晨09:00 战斗就将打响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为保护奥布而战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是选择其他道路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要自己作出判断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此如果有人想提前下船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以立即离开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按奥布政府的指示前往避难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我这个没用的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗到今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见穿着这身衣服的人慌慌张张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布要变成战场了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布选择的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管可能荆棘丛生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 卡嘉莉也镇静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管行不行 我会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像父亲他们那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基…基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 听我说 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 卡兹要走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 赛不走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留下 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受攻击的 是奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且现在 我也有能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚给家里打过电话 和他们说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 米丽会下船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡兹 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别总在乎别人的想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己决定的 有什么好在乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人情况不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只有我一个人下船的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会有人说我是胆小鬼 自私
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡兹 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道肯定会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…不像你这么能干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事应该让有本事的人去做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 只是不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人太善良
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等和平了 我们再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了 要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了别说了 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候又会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审问？ 押送？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船又得参加战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军打到奥布来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 没你事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军来进攻 大天使号要参战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留你在船上没用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以快下船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想知道你们为什么跟地球军打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为奥布不肯和地球军联手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么 自然人都傻？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击开始后会很乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 自己照顾好自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得轻松…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 暴风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西本来就是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曙光社领走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我们也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你也要去打仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是负责大天使号CIC的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是奥布人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上属不当要求 无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布联合首长国仍会坚持中立国立场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真不愧是阿斯哈前代表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不会让人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才还在担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要是接受了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那些宝贝的测试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他们多坚持一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉声叹气的干什么呢 舰长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后也只有11个人下船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都挺有骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能为JOSHI-A的事耿耿于怀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 你为什么回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在JOSH-A
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被你这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我 讨厌机动堡垒驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 我现在是机动战士驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来难以避免
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布和地球军的开战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们会轻易为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布和地球军为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特算什么 我长大了杀光他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科雷！ 十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特占领卡本塔里亚时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他失去了父母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扩大战火很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但扑灭却难上加难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰巡航导弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布全军 开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布军  开始战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱 交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由罗 左边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈特弗里德瞄准 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱丽 是地球军的机动战士部队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人机动战士部队 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伊佐那岐海岸登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调第八机甲大队过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自凝岛上空 出现大型飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和 自由 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 请出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆·拉·弗拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,质量加速器和曙光工厂不许弄坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他随便打是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢 帅哥酷毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是个新兵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 再发呆敌人就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏瑞安 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干那个 白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人机动战士 不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动堡垒 接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏了 臭枪法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的新型机？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击灭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 抹杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是负责大天使号CIC的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是奥布人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事 夏尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱网 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退后 大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由…基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰相信为之而战的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是获得的勋章吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是父亲的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我长大了杀光他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为熟悉的世界 构造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括 扣下扳机的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前炮火中驰骋的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是曾经的伙伴 还是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破碎的过去被唤醒时
